title: Kaxapa Factory
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Venezuelan, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Kaxapa is a Venezuelan corn cake or tortilla made with fresh corn instead of masa. It is served with a filling of your choice like a taco. Also offers arepa and patacones. Owners knows what vegan means. Try the Kaxapa la vegana, veggie arepa, or the patacones with grilled veggies. 2015 relocated from Constituyentes.
